    "OpenClient connects to your LiteLLM for privacy-first access to any AI." : {
      "comment" : "A description of OpenClient's privacy-first connection to LiteLLM.",
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "value" : "OpenClientはプライバシー重視でLiteLLMに接続し、あらゆるAIにアクセスします。",
